-- Fondiaria-Sai May Merge With Premafin, Unipol Gruppo, Il Sole Reports
-- B y   A r m o r e l   K e n n a
-- 2011-12-31T11:56:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-31/fondiaria-sai-may-merge-with-premafin-unipol-gruppo-il-sole-reports.html
Fondiaria-Sai SpA (FSA)  may merge with its
holding company Premafin Finanziaria SpA, and  Unipol Gruppo
Finanziario SpA (UNI) , daily Il Sole 24 Ore reported, without saying
where it obtained the information.  Investors may buy shares in a capital increase of more than
1 billion euros ($1.3 billion,) according to the newspaper.
Clessidra SGR SpA, an Italian private-equity fund, is ready to
invest 200 million euros, Sole reported.  Assets, including Unipol Banca, may be sold after a merger,
the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Armorel Kenna in Milan at 
